<p>得到线性模型</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>⋅</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
w_1\cdot x+b_1=3x^{(1)}+3x^{(2)}+1
